Calendar - Class in com.phonegap.calendar.android.adapters

com.phonegap.calendar.android.adapters - package com.phonegap.calendar.android.adapters
All classes into com.phonegap.calendar.android.adapters package are implemented in order to make easier the use of the library, here we can obtain object with all the info supported by model layer and the operations that those objects have to perform, it could be considered like an abstraction layer in a higher level adding some business operations.
